name: Ricky Iwasaki
title: Injineli yesoftware
summary: Umphuhlisi weSoftware onamava, ofuna ithuba elitsha lokusebenzela iiprojekthi ezinkulu. Unomdla ekudaleni okanye ekongezeni ikhowudi ukuze abanye bayisebenzise. Ndiyakholelwa ukuba izakhono zam zincinci xa kuthelekiswa ne-intanethi, ngoko ke ndinomdla kakhulu ekusebenzeni nezinye izixhobo, iinkonzo, iilwimi zeprogram.

experience.title: Injineli yesoftware
responsibilities: Yakhiwe kwaye yaphunyezwa usetyenziso lwewebhu olunokwehla kusetyenziswa iReact kunye neNode.js
Ukusebenzisana nabaphathi beemveliso ukucokisa iimfuno kunye nokuqinisekisa ukuhanjiswa kwangexesha
Kuphuhliswe kwaye kugcinwe i-RESTful APIs kwizicelo zewebhu
Izikripthi eziphuhlisiwe ukuze zizenzele imisebenzi kunye nokuphucula ukusebenza kakuhle

experience.title: Umqeqeshi weTennis oNcedisayo
responsibilities: Ukufundisa ubuchule bentenetya kwisethingi yeqela labadlali aba-5-10
Ukwenza isifundo sibe mnandi kwaye sibe nolonwabo kubadlali
Inoxanduva lokhuseleko lwabadlali enkundleni, ngakumbi abadlali abancinci nabadala, abafana nabaneminyaka emi-3 kunye nabaneminyaka engama-60 ubudala.

experience.title: Umhlobo Wangaphandle
responsibilities: Ukugcina indawo yokugcina icocekile kwaye icwangcisiwe
Ukugcina imeko ekhuselekileyo nenobubele kubathengi nabasebenzi

projects.name: Ipotfoliyo
projects.description: Iwebhusayithi ephendulayo ebonisa iiprojekthi kunye nezakhono usebenzisa itekhnoloji yewebhu yanamhlanje
